<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSavage-Smith1985">Savage-Smith, Emilie (1985), <i>Islamicate Celestial Globes: Their History, Construction, and Use</i>, Smithsonian Institution Press, Washington, D.C.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Islamicate+Celestial+Globes%3A+Their+History%2C+Construction%2C+and+Use&amp;rft.aulast=Savage-Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Emilie&amp;rft.au=Savage-Smith%2C+Emilie&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.pub=Smithsonian+Institution+Press%2C+Washington%2C+D.C.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Armillary_sphere"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
